## Project Description

CASCI (CI/CD Application Server for Continuous Integration) is a complete CI/CD platform in a single static Go binary (400-500MB) that replaces Jenkins, GitHub Actions, GitLab CI, CircleCI, Travis CI, and other CI/CD tools.

**Key Features:**
- Single static binary - zero dependencies (CGO_ENABLED=0)
- Zero configuration required (database-driven)
- 100% Jenkins API compatible
- Runs ALL CI/CD formats unchanged
- Built-in security scanning (embedded tools)
- Self-healing architecture
- Scales from laptop to 1000+ nodes
- Target cost: $83/year operation

---

