## Build & Release (BASE.md Compliant)

### Makefile Targets (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- `build` - Build all platforms to `./binaries/`
- `release` - GitHub release to `./releases/`
- `docker` - Docker release for ARM64/AMD64
- `test` - Run all tests

### Binary Naming (NON-NEGOTIABLE)
- Local/Testing: `/tmp/casci`
- Host Build: `./binaries/casci`
- Distribution: `casci-{os}-{arch}` (strip -musl from filenames)

### Build Requirements
- Single static binary with `CGO_ENABLED=0`
- Embedded assets using Go embed
- Build command: `go build -o /tmp/casci ./src/cmd/casci`

