## Technical Architecture Notes

### Database Strategy
- Default: SQLite (single file)
- With external DB: Database is source of truth
- Config file synced from database (one-way)
- Optimistic locking for conflicts (last write wins with warning)

### Build System
- Single static binary with CGO_ENABLED=0
- Embedded assets using Go embed
- Multi-platform: Linux, BSD, macOS, Windows (AMD64, ARM64)
- Must use modernc.org/sqlite (pure Go, not go-sqlite3)

### Security & Authentication
- Bcrypt for passwords
- JWT for sessions (24h expiry)
- API token authentication
- First user becomes administrator

### Port Strategy
- Default: Random unused port in 64xxx range
- Single port: HTTP only
- Dual port (e.g., "8080,64453"): HTTP + HTTPS
- Special case: "80,443" triggers Let's Encrypt

