CASCI (CI/CD Application Server for Continuous Integration) represents a fundamental reimagining of CI/CD infrastructure. Instead of the current landscape of fragmented tools, plugins, and services, CASCI provides a single static binary that encompasses all CI/CD functionality while maintaining 100% compatibility with existing workflows.


