## File System Layout

### Directory Structure

```yaml
System Directories:

/usr/local/bin/
  casci                     # Main binary

/etc/casci/
  /security/                # Security databases only
    /merged/
      geoip.mmdb           # Deduplicated GeoIP (200MB)
      cve.db               # Deduplicated CVEs (500MB)
      malware.db           # Deduplicated signatures (300MB)
    /cache/                # Temporary downloads

/var/lib/casci/
  casci.db                 # SQLite database (if used)
  /scanners/               # Extracted security tools
    trivy                  # Container scanner
    gitleaks               # Secret scanner
    semgrep                # SAST scanner
  /artifacts/              # Build artifacts
    /{user}/{project}/{build}/
      artifact.tar.gz
      metadata.json
  /workspaces/             # Build workspaces
    /{node}/{build}/
      (build files)
  /cache/                  # Build cache
    /docker/               # Docker layer cache
    /dependencies/         # Dependency cache
    /ccache/               # C/C++ compilation cache

/var/log/casci/
  casci.log                # Main application log
  builds.log               # Build execution log
  security.log             # Security scanning log
  audit.log                # Audit trail
  database.log             # Database operations
  scheduler.log            # Scheduled tasks
  updates.log              # Security DB updates
  api.log                  # API requests
  webhook.log              # Webhook events
  /builds/                 # Individual build logs
    /{user}/
      build-{id}.log
  /users/                  # User-specific logs
    /{user}/
      api.log
      /security/
      /deploys/
```

### Storage Management

```yaml
Storage Policies:

Artifacts:
  Default retention: 30 days
  User configurable: 1-365 days
  Automatic cleanup: Daily at 3 AM
  Compression: gzip by default
  Deduplication: Content-based

Build Logs:
  Default retention: 90 days
  User logs: Last 100 builds
  Compression: After 7 days
  Rotation: Weekly

Workspaces:
  Cleanup: Immediately after build
  Failed builds: Keep 24 hours
  Cache: LRU eviction at 80% disk

Security Databases:
  Update: Daily
  Deduplication: After each update
  Compression: ZSTD
  Total size: ~1GB after dedup
```

