### Build Isolation

```yaml
Network Isolation:

Linux:
  - Create casci0 dummy interface
  - Builds get dedicated network namespace
  - Internet access only (no LAN)
  - Rate limiting available
  - Traffic monitoring

Process Isolation:
  - Containers: Full isolation
  - Native: Process groups
  - Resource limits enforced
  - No access to host processes

File System Isolation:
  - Chroot/pivot_root for containers
  - Temporary workspace
  - Read-only bind mounts
  - No access to host filesystem
  - Cleanup guaranteed
```

